{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"工具","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">CSS提供了许多强大的功能，但这些功能要么可能很难使用，要么有许多参数，因此在使用它们时，能够可视化它们是有帮助的。此页面提供了一些有用的工具的链接，这些工具将帮助您使用这些功能构建 CSS 来设计您的内容。</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"row topicpage-table\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect3\"><dl><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"sect4\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts_25d4b407d3e5044aeffb97faa9669a95\"><basefont></a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">HTML 标签&lt;basefont&gt;用来设置文档的默认字体大小。使用<code>font</code>可以相对于默认字体大小进行变化。</dd><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"htmlbasefontelement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts\">HTMLBaseFontElement</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">The <strong><code>HTMLBaseFontElement</code></strong> interface provides special properties (beyond the regular <code>HTMLElement</code> interface it also has available to it by inheritance) for manipulating <code>basefont</code> elements.</dd></dl></dl></div>\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect5\"><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"using_url_values_for_the_cursor_property\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/cursor\">Using URL values for the cursor property</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Gecko\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Gecko</a> 1.8 (Firefox 1.5，SeaMonkey 1.0) 支持CSS的URL值&nbsp;<code>cursor</code> 属性在Windows和Linux。Mac支持是在Gecko 2（Firefox 4）中添加的。这允许将任意图像指定为鼠标光标 - 可以使用Gecko支持的任何图像格式。</dd></dl></div>\n    </div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"其他工具","title":"其他工具","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>CSS 动画- <a href=\"http://jeremyckahn.github.io/stylie/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Stylie</a></li>\n <li>查看设备的显示信息(从 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\">响应式网页设计</a>处得到帮助) - <a href=\"http://mydevice.io\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">mydevice.io</a></li>\n <li>CSS 菜单-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cssmenumaker.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">cssmenumaker.com</a></li>\n <li>一个 强大并现代化的 CSS linter 可以帮助你实现统一约定并避免样式表中的错误 - <a href=\"https://stylelint.io/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">stylelint</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关主题","title":"相关主题","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"其他工具","id":"其他工具"},{"text":"相关主题","id":"相关主题"}],"summary":"","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Tools","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Herramientas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"ツール","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Ferramentas","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/css","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/css/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"工具 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}